title: 2015–16 FC Banants season
text:
The 2015–16 season was <a href="FC%20Urartu">Banants</a>'s 15th season in the <a href="Armenian%20Premier%20League">Armenian Premier League</a>. They finished the season sixth in the <a href="2015%E2%80%9316%20Armenian%20Premier%20League">league</a>, whilst they also won the <a href="2015%E2%80%9316%20Armenian%20Cup">Armenian Cup</a>, earning entry in to the <a href="2016%E2%80%9317%20UEFA%20Europa%20League">UEFA Europa League</a> at the first qualifying stage.
Season events.
At the end of the season, Albert Ohanyan, Soslan Kalmanov, Andrey Shahgeldyan, <a href="Miguel%20Pedro%20L%C3%B3pez">Miguel López</a> and <a href="Denis%20Mahmudov">Denis Mahmudov</a> were all released by the club.
